abstract: Yanina Wickmayer beats Karin Knapp and Lauren Davis beats Ajla Tomljanovic in first round of the Nottingham Open; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: Karin Knapp, the fourth seed, and Ajla Tomljanovic, the eighth seed, lost in the first round.
